    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK845">
<l>kallāta mēṟkoṇ ṭoḻukal kacaṭaṟa</l>
<l>vallatūu maiyan tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Fools pretending to know what has not been read (by them) will rouse suspicion even as to what they have thoroughly mastered.</l>
